1
00:00:09,250 --> 00:00:11,369
Mwongeye guhabwa ikaze!
Iki ni icyumweru  cya gatatu,

2
00:00:11,370 --> 00:00:12,974
Kwamamaza Ukwihangira imirimo,

3
00:00:12,975 --> 00:00:16,239
Iki cyumweru muzumva ibijyanye 
n'uburyo bwo kubikora neza

4
00:00:16,239 --> 00:00:18,514
Bituma kwamamaza kwawe kugenda neza,

5
00:00:18,515 --> 00:00:20,896
Bizafasha kampani yawe gutera intambwe ,

6
00:00:20,897 --> 00:00:23,586
hanyuma bikazatuma ibikorwa byawe bigenda neza ku masoko,

7
00:00:23,587 --> 00:00:28,376
ni ukuvuga ko uri mu nzira yo gukora ubucuruzi 
buzaramba kandi bifite ubuzima.

8
00:00:28,380 --> 00:00:31,173
Hari ibintu bibiri 
tuzajyaho impaka muri iki cyumweru

9
00:00:31,174 --> 00:00:35,039
Ariko igice cya mbere turajya impaka, bikunze
kuri kimwe muri byo cy'ingenzi,

10
00:00:35,128 --> 00:00:37,707
Aricyo guteza imbere 
uburyo ukoresha wamamaza.

11
00:00:37,708 --> 00:00:41,905
Iterembere ry'uburyo uteza imbere kwamamaza 
ni kimwe mu bikorwa bisaba ko ubutegura.

12
00:00:41,906 --> 00:00:44,383
ugomba gucamo
mu gihe urema ibikorwa 

13
00:00:44,384 --> 00:00:49,962
Reka twibuke ko isoko,
Ni ukuvuga abakiriya ku isoko,

14
00:00:49,963 --> 00:00:52,992
Bizishyura
imiremere yo kurema kampani yawe,

15
00:00:52,993 --> 00:00:55,822
kandi kuko bakunda ibicuruzwa byawe,
bazabigura

16
00:00:55,834 --> 00:00:58,779
kandi ayo mafaranga azaza 
muri kampani nk'atembera.

17
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:01,686
Mu gihe utekereza ku buryo bwo guteza imbere
kwamamaza,

18
00:01:01,687 --> 00:01:04,248
kimwe mu bintu 
ugomba gufataho umwanzuro

19
00:01:04,248 --> 00:01:07,291
Ni igice cy'isoko uba ugamije
uba ukeneye kwitaho,

20
00:01:07,292 --> 00:01:09,933
ikindi cy'ingenzi
ukeneye gufataho umwanzuro

21
00:01:09,934 --> 00:01:12,627
Ni ukuntu igice cy'abakiriya uzibandaho
bazabona igicuruzwa cyawe


22
00:01:12,628 --> 00:01:15,124
bagereranyije n'iby'abo muhanganye 

23
00:01:15,125 --> 00:01:19,397
reka dusubire inyuma ku byo twagiyeho impaka
mu gice cy'intangiriro cy'iki cyumweru

24
00:01:19,398 --> 00:01:21,258
Ku kwamamaza ukwihangira imirimo

25
00:01:21,259 --> 00:01:23,954
Aho twabahaye imikorere ifatika,

26
00:01:23,955 --> 00:01:26,327
reka mbibutse uburyo imikorere

27
00:01:26,328 --> 00:01:28,665
hanyuma ndabereka 
ibyo tuzakora muri iki gice.

28
00:01:28,666 --> 00:01:30,478
Iby'ingenzi ni ibi bikurikira:

29
00:01:38,561 --> 00:01:40,749
Wubakiye kuri uriya musingi wafata umwanzuro

30
00:01:40,750 --> 00:01:44,598
Ese ni ikihe gice kibona
inyungu nyinshi mu gicuruzwa cyawe,

31
00:01:44,599 --> 00:01:48,754
ndetse n'uko abakiriya 
muri icyo gice wibanzeho

32
00:01:48,755 --> 00:01:51,154
bakabaye babona kampani yawe.

33
00:01:51,155 --> 00:01:56,513
Ikindi gice cyakabaye 
uburyo bupanze neza.

34
00:01:57,481 --> 00:02:02,330
bisobanura uko umwanya wakabaye ushyirwamo,
ese isoko wibandaho ni irihe.

35
00:02:12,214 --> 00:02:16,453
ibi tubyita umwanzuro wo mu byiciro
n'umwanzuro uguha umwanya,

36
00:02:16,454 --> 00:02:19,856
nk'uko nabiberetse
ibi bice by'ingenzi, umwanzuro wateguwe

37
00:02:19,857 --> 00:02:24,150
ukoraho mu gihe uri gukora ku buryo uteza 
imbere uburyo bwo kwamamaza.

38
00:02:34,142 --> 00:02:36,170
Ushingiye kuri ubu buryo bubiri
bwo gufata imyanzuro

39
00:02:36,171 --> 00:02:39,635
Uzaba ushobora gufata imyanzuro 
ku bindi bibazo

40
00:02:39,636 --> 00:02:41,725
bigusaba gukora,

41
00:02:41,726 --> 00:02:45,049
Ku buryo mu gice cyo gushyira mu bikorwa 
uburyo uzakoresha wamamaza.

42
00:02:45,222 --> 00:02:49,036
Bamwe muri mwe bashobora kuba barumvise
uburyo bwo kwamamaza buvanze.

43
00:02:49,261 --> 00:02:52,576
Neza neza ibyo bice byaba
ibyihariye cyane,

44
00:02:52,577 --> 00:02:54,404
Ibyo gushyira mu bikorwa.

45
00:03:07,134 --> 00:03:10,386
Ivangavanga ryo kwamamaza
ndetse n'ishyirwa mu bikorwa rikurikira 

46
00:03:14,701 --> 00:03:17,241
byo tuza kuba tujyaho impaka
ni zirindwi za P

47
00:03:17,242 --> 00:03:18,877
Zikaba ari izaguwe za P kane

48
00:03:18,878 --> 00:03:21,864
no kwita cyane 
ku ikorwa rya serivisi

49
00:03:22,167 --> 00:03:24,288
ndetse na bimwe mu bibazo 
byo gushyira mu bikorwa

50
00:03:24,289 --> 00:03:25,943
Nka kwamamaza kwa Guerrilla, n;ibibdi.

51
00:03:25,944 --> 00:03:28,517
Ariko ikintu kimwe ni ingenzi:
ukeneye kumva itandukaniro

52
00:03:28,518 --> 00:03:33,011
riri hagati y'ibikorwa biteguye
n'ishyirwa mu bikorwa ryabyo.

53
00:03:33,012 --> 00:03:36,796
Iki ni ikintu benshi muri ba rwiyemezamirimo
bakora ariko nti babone icyo bifuzaga

54
00:03:36,797 --> 00:03:41,284
bakagomba gukosora no gukosora
uburyo babishyize mu bikorwa.

55
00:03:41,285 --> 00:03:45,281
Iyo utekereje ku kwamamaza,
ugomba kubitekerezaho,

56
00:03:45,282 --> 00:03:46,847
ko hari uburyo buteguye kuri yo,

57
00:03:46,848 --> 00:03:49,821
kandi hari uburyo bunyuranye bwo kubishyira mu bikorwa
uburyo bwo kubikora

58
00:03:49,822 --> 00:03:51,835
Ikintu cya 
mbere ugomba kumva

59
00:03:51,836 --> 00:03:54,686
Ni imihatanire itandukanye y'ibyo ukora.

60
00:03:55,279 --> 00:03:56,851
Kubera iki ibi ari ingenzi?

61
00:03:56,852 --> 00:04:01,015
Kuko imihatanire y'ibyo ukora
ikwemerera gushyiraho ibirenze

62
00:04:01,016 --> 00:04:02,788
ugererenyije n'abo muhanganye.

63
00:04:02,789 --> 00:04:05,678
Hagomba kubaho ikintu ugomba kuba
uzi gukora muri kampani yawe.

64
00:04:05,679 --> 00:04:07,637
Tekereza ku mihatanire yawe.

65
00:04:07,638 --> 00:04:12,707
Niba wowe nk'umuntu,
uri gukora akazi hariya,

66
00:04:12,708 --> 00:04:16,986
ukeneye kuba udasanzwe, uba ukeneye
kuba ushobora byinshi

67
00:04:16,987 --> 00:04:20,516
abandi bantu bakora 
akazi nk'ako ukora badafite.

68
00:04:20,517 --> 00:04:22,280
kugirango ubone ako kazi,

69
00:04:22,281 --> 00:04:24,959
kandi hari imitekerereze ikora aho no
mu gukora ibikorwa bishya

70
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:27,902
ukeneye gushaka
kampani ikora neza

71
00:04:28,430 --> 00:04:33,276
ibicuruzwa bikoranye
ubwenge bwinshi, ubushobozi,

72
00:04:33,860 --> 00:04:36,375
hanyuma uba ufute ukintu
cyo gutwara ku isoko

73
00:04:36,376 --> 00:04:38,882
aho abakiriya bazavuga bati,
" Yego, iki gicuruzwa ni ingenzi cyane!

74
00:04:38,883 --> 00:04:40,992
ni impano ikomeye batuzaniye,

75
00:04:41,682 --> 00:04:45,981
kandi ndagihitamo ngereranyije 
n'icyo abo muhanganye bafite."

76
00:04:45,982 --> 00:04:48,484
muri iyo nzira, iby'ingenzi by'ibikorwa

77
00:04:48,485 --> 00:04:51,928
by'uko wamamaza
bijyana

78
00:04:51,929 --> 00:04:54,238
no kumenya icyo ugomba kwibandaho,

79
00:04:54,239 --> 00:04:57,059
kandi uba ukeneye kubyumva 
kare ugitangira kurema ibikorwa byawe.

80
00:04:57,060 --> 00:04:58,998
iyo dutekereje ku
 mihatanire itandukanye

81
00:04:58,999 --> 00:05:00,411
bishobora kuba ari ibintu byinshi

82
00:05:00,412 --> 00:05:03,049
Mu bikorwa bikoresha ikoranabuhanga rihanitse,
aba ari ikoranabuhanga,

83
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:07,639
iba ikoranye udushya, nshya
kandi ifite ibice byinshi kuri yo.

84
00:05:07,640 --> 00:05:11,690
itanga serivisi
andi makoranabihanga atakora.

85
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:17,908
ariko bishobora no kuba uko bikoze neza,
bifite ubuziranenge, kwita ku bakiriya.

86
00:05:17,909 --> 00:05:20,264
ubundi iyo turebye
ku mitangirire mizima,

87
00:05:20,265 --> 00:05:23,997
Ni imvange y'ibyo byose ndetse n'ibindi.

88
00:05:23,998 --> 00:05:25,842
Kubera iki aha?

89
00:05:26,492 --> 00:05:31,237
Kuko abandi bakora, abo muhanganye
bizabagora kukwigana,

90
00:05:31,238 --> 00:05:33,077
bigana ibyo uzaba ukora

91
00:05:33,078 --> 00:05:37,642
niba uguhatana kwawe
gushingiye ku bintu byinshi.

92
00:05:38,882 --> 00:05:41,499
Biba bigoye kureba ibyo uba ukora,

93
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:43,175
kandi bikaba binakomeye kukwigana,

94
00:05:43,176 --> 00:05:47,186
Igihe ufite umutwato
y'ibyo ushobora wubakiyeho,

95
00:05:47,946 --> 00:05:53,424
uba ufite intambwe imbere
uba urusha abo muhanganye.

96
00:05:53,425 --> 00:05:54,740
Uko kumva

97
00:05:54,741 --> 00:05:57,662
ko ushoboye byinshi binyuranye
no guhangana binyuranye

98
00:05:57,663 --> 00:06:02,257
bizagukorera intangiriro
ku yindi myanzuro yo kwamamaza uzafata,

99
00:06:02,258 --> 00:06:07,519
iy'ingenzi, iyo mwakoreye gahunda,
kandi n'indi ituma ibikorwa bikomeza,

100
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:09,863
Ikibazo cyo kubishyira mu bikorwa
twagiyeho impaka mbere.

101
00:06:09,864 --> 00:06:12,212
Igice cyo gufata imyanzuro
gisubiza ikibazo,

102
00:06:12,213 --> 00:06:13,914
"Ese ni irihe soko mfite?"

103
00:06:13,915 --> 00:06:16,673
Mu gihe umwanzuro wo kwiha umwanya
usubiza ikibazo,

104
00:06:16,674 --> 00:06:20,437
"Ese kuki abantu bo mu isoko nibandaho
bazagura ibicuruzwa byanjye cyangwa serivisi

105
00:06:20,438 --> 00:06:22,078
aho kugurira abo duhatana?"

106
00:06:22,079 --> 00:06:26,364
Uhita ubona iko imyanzuro yo guca ibice n'iyo kwiha uwanya

107
00:06:26,365 --> 00:06:28,618
ari impande ebyiri ku giceri kimwe.

108
00:06:28,619 --> 00:06:30,838
Niyo mpamvu byakabaye
 byerekanwa neza

109
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:34,332
Reka tubirebe neza birambuye
kugirango tubafashe kumva neza ibyo bivuga.

110
00:06:34,615 --> 00:06:36,350
Reka dutangirane n'igice cyo guca ibice

111
00:06:36,351 --> 00:06:38,626
Ba rwiyemezamirimo benshi
bakorana n'igice kimwe.

112
00:06:38,627 --> 00:06:42,461
Ibi ni uko baba bafite ibyo bakeneye bidahagije.

113
00:06:43,761 --> 00:06:48,031
Ba rwiyemezamirimo bashobora kuvuga,
" Ndinjira ibice binyuranye icyarimwe,"

114
00:06:48,032 --> 00:06:51,985
Ariko ibi byakorwa gusa iyo hari
imikoranire ikomeye hagati y'uduce.

115
00:06:51,986 --> 00:06:54,813
Akenshi jya ureba igice kimwe

116
00:06:54,814 --> 00:06:57,784
Kandi icyo gice kiba gikwiye kwitbabwaho cyane nawe.

117
00:06:58,734 --> 00:07:02,203
Kuko hari ibyo abakiriya 
baba basaba ibice binyuranye.

118
00:07:02,204 --> 00:07:06,024
Uba ukeneye kwinjira muri icyo gice neza
ugashimisha abakiriya

119
00:07:06,025 --> 00:07:09,020
baba bavuga iby'ibicuruzwa byawe
mu buryo bubashimishije

120
00:07:09,021 --> 00:07:10,807
ugerageza kurema amagambo mashya.

121
00:07:10,808 --> 00:07:14,663
igice cyo hagati mu guca ibice ni
" Abakiriya bawe ni abahe?"

122
00:07:15,763 --> 00:07:18,828
Wubakira kuri icyo kibazo
kandi uba ufite ibindi bibazp byiyongeraho

123
00:07:18,829 --> 00:07:22,459
uba ukeneye kurebaho
no gusubiza kugirango ubashe kumva

124
00:07:22,460 --> 00:07:26,382
niba igice wahisemo
ari cyo cyiza mu by'ukuri, yego?

125
00:07:26,389 --> 00:07:32,967
Ikibazo cya mbere cyakuyobora kuri iyi ntangiriro
yo kwiha umwanya no guca ibice

126
00:07:32,968 --> 00:07:36,976
ni imyanzuro ibiri ifitanye isano
yagafatiwe neza hamwe

127
00:07:36,977 --> 00:07:38,617
kuko bigusaba,

128
00:07:38,618 --> 00:07:40,985
" Niba inyungu yabonetse
abo bagisemo mu gutanga imyanya

129
00:07:40,986 --> 00:07:43,908
ihura n'ikenewe
n'igice cy'abakiriya?"

130
00:07:44,503 --> 00:07:46,911
Hakenewe kubaho ukubiringaniza.

131
00:07:46,912 --> 00:07:51,209
Ikindi kibazo cy'ingenzi ni
" Ese ni gute byanyorohera kugera ku bice byanjye?

132
00:07:51,210 --> 00:07:53,688
Igice cy'abakiriya gifite ubushobozi bwo kugura ibintu bingana iki

133
00:07:53,689 --> 00:07:57,799
kandi ugerageje kureba kure
ese impinduka zishoboka ziri mu gice

134
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:02,814
bishobora kugira ingaruka ku migurire y'abakiriya
ndetse n'ibindi bigize icyo gice,

135
00:08:02,815 --> 00:08:05,441
Ni ukuvuga, ushobora kuyigira ikurura abakiriya 
cyangwa idakurura kuru wowe?

136
00:08:05,442 --> 00:08:07,309
Bwanyuma ushobora gushaka gutekereza

137
00:08:07,310 --> 00:08:10,650
ku bikorwa by'abo muhatanye
 muri iki gice kimwe

138
00:08:10,651 --> 00:08:13,666
hano hari urutonde wareberaho imitsindire yo gukata ibice.

139
00:08:13,667 --> 00:08:16,853
Imigaburire y'ibice yakagombye kuba

140
00:08:16,854 --> 00:08:21,093
ahaba hari urusange
rw'ibikenerwa n'ibishakwa mu gice,

141
00:08:21,094 --> 00:08:24,784
n'uruvangitirane
rw'ibikenerwa n'ibishakwa hagati mu gice.

142
00:08:24,785 --> 00:08:27,641
iyi foto iravuga mu 
by'ukuri muri icyo cyerekezo,

143
00:08:27,642 --> 00:08:32,104
Kuko urabona abantu batatu hano,
bose bambaye imipira itukura,

144
00:08:32,105 --> 00:08:35,241
bose bafite indorerwamo zera,
bafite ubwanwa bungana kandi bumwe

145
00:08:35,241 --> 00:08:37,623
biyogoshesheje kimwe,
ndetse banamwenyura kimwe.

146
00:08:37,624 --> 00:08:39,309
bashobora kuba baravukiye icyarimwe,

147
00:08:39,311 --> 00:08:43,014
Ariko ndatekerezako bafashe ifoto y'umwe
 bakayikoramo eshatu icyarimwe.

148
00:08:43,486 --> 00:08:47,230
Muri iyo njyana, ni iki gishimishije

149
00:08:47,231 --> 00:08:49,555
ni uko uvuye,
muko kampani ibibona,

150
00:08:49,556 --> 00:08:52,381
kureba iki gice hano,
aba bantu

151
00:08:52,382 --> 00:08:56,644
Uzaviga uti, " Ni byo, nzi neza 
icyo bakeneye, icyo bashaka,

152
00:08:56,645 --> 00:08:59,120
Birasa,
ni bimwe"

153
00:08:59,121 --> 00:09:02,139
Biguhesha ubushobozi
bwo kugira ubutumwa woherereza abakiriya

154
00:09:02,140 --> 00:09:05,553
iki kiba gifite intego
kuko uba uzi ibyo bakeneye.

155
00:09:05,554 --> 00:09:08,208
Iyo bari kuba none abantu banyuranye,

156
00:09:08,908 --> 00:09:12,256
umwe yambaye umupira w'ubururu,
undi yambaye usa icyatsi kibisi,

157
00:09:12,257 --> 00:09:14,190
washoboraga kugira
 ibihe bikomeye mu kuvuga,

158
00:09:14,191 --> 00:09:18,239
" Yego, ese mpaza ibyo abakiriya bakeneye?"

159
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:21,133
Ibi bishobora kugaruka,
kuri wowe ukaba wavuga

160
00:09:21,134 --> 00:09:26,452
Ndashaka ibicuruzwa binyuranye muko bingana, ndetse n'uko bikoze."

161
00:09:26,453 --> 00:09:28,377
Undi akeneye ubundi bwoko bw'ibicuruzwa,

162
00:09:28,378 --> 00:09:31,562
Ibyo birakwica
kuko bikomeye.

163
00:09:32,742 --> 00:09:38,750
igice cyiza rereo cyakabaye gifite uduce amatandukaniro muri buri gace

164
00:09:38,751 --> 00:09:41,481
n'amatandukaniro akomeye ku bindi bice.

165
00:09:41,482 --> 00:09:45,785
wakabaye kandi ushobora
kureba ingano y'ibice byawe.

166
00:09:45,786 --> 00:09:47,934
niba udashobora kumenye ingano y'ibice byawe,

167
00:09:47,935 --> 00:09:52,145
bizaba bigaragaza 
ko utigeze ucamo ibice neza.

168
00:09:53,335 --> 00:09:55,643
kandi, ibice
byakabaye binini bihagije.

169
00:09:55,644 --> 00:09:58,279
kugirango kampani 
ibashe kubibonamo inyungu

170
00:09:58,280 --> 00:10:01,774
ibyo bice 
biguha urutonde rwo kureberaho,

171
00:10:01,775 --> 00:10:06,189
ariko tekereza by'ibanze, gerageza gutekereza
ku nyungu uzashyiraho

172
00:10:06,190 --> 00:10:10,101
Uvuga, " iri ni isoko ryanjye nzibandaho
aba bantu ndabazi,

173
00:10:10,102 --> 00:10:13,793
Nzi ubwoko bw'ubutumwa
 bw'iyamamaza bubashimisha,"

174
00:10:13,794 --> 00:10:17,354
Kuko bavuze biriya, wababwira ibi,
abo bantu bazagaruka bavuga,

175
00:10:17,355 --> 00:10:22,242
" Yego,! narahagijwe n'ibyo nari nkeneye.
binyuze mu butumwa mwatanze mwamamaza.

176
00:10:22,243 --> 00:10:24,103
Mureke ngure igicuruzwa cyanyu."

177
00:10:24,104 --> 00:10:28,026
Igice cy'ingenzi gishimishije cyo gucamo ibice,
ni ukwamamaza ukoresheje telefoni zigendanwa.

178
00:10:28,027 --> 00:10:32,500
Hari ibintu byinshi bigira uruhare
mu gufata imyanzuro yo guca ibice muri iri soko.

179
00:10:32,501 --> 00:10:35,043
Urugero, gutandukanya abantu ugendeye uko bitwara,
utibagiwe ibyo bakunda

180
00:10:35,084 --> 00:10:40,617
imyifatire y'umukiriya nk'iteye impungenge cyane mu gice cyo guca isoko mo ibice.

181
00:10:40,897 --> 00:10:43,531
ariko n'ibiranga abantu bitewe n'aho baturuka
n'amatsinda yabo

